OL,3,CFormer pupil at UK school confirmed
OL,4,Cdead after fire at Swiss ski resort
OL,6,FThe fire at the Crans-Montana resort
OL,7,Fin Switzerland killed 40 people on New
OL,8,FYear's Day, as ITV News' Amy Lewis
OL,9,Freports
OL,11,FA former pupil at a British school has
OL,12,Fbeen confirmed to have died after a
OL,13,Ffire at a Swiss ski resort killed 40
OL,14,Fpeople and injured 119 others.
OL,16,FCharlotte Niddam, 15, was among the
OL,17,Flast 16 victims to have been
OL,18,Fidentified by police after the New
OL,19,FYear blaze at the Crans-Montana resort.
