OL,6,FShe was initially reported as missing
OL,7,Fafter a fire broke out inside the
OL,8,FConstellation bar in the early hours
OL,9,Fof Thursday, while revellers were
OL,10,Fcelebrating the start of 2026.
OL,12,FIn a social media post on Sunday,
OL,13,FCharlotte's family said: "It is with
OL,14,Fgreat sadness that we announce the
OL,15,Fpassing of our beautiful daughter and
OL,16,Fsister Charlotte.
OL,18,F"Details regarding the funeral
OL,19,Farrangements will follow shortly."
