OL,6,FThe post said Charlotte's funeral is
OL,7,Fexpected to take place in Paris later
OL,8,Fthis week.
OL,10,FCharlotte attended Immanuel College in
OL,11,FHertfordshire, according to multiple
OL,12,Freports, and after the fire, the
OL,13,Fschool said in a statement it was
OL,14,F"praying for a miracle".
OL,16,FAccording to the Crans-Montana resort
OL,17,Fwebsite, Charlotte had been working as
OL,18,Fa babysitter in the area.
OL,20,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper
OL,21,Fconfirmed the news in a post on X.
