OL,6,FShe said: "Terrible news that
OL,7,FCharlotte Niddam has been identified
OL,8,Fas one of those killed in the Crans-
OL,9,FMontana fire.
OL,11,F"My thoughts are with all her family
OL,12,Fand friends after this devastating
OL,13,Floss."
OL,15,FAll 40 people killed in the fire have
OL,16,Fnow been identified, the Valais region
OL,17,Fpolice force said on Sunday.
