OL,6,FThe last 16 victims included two Swiss
OL,7,Fgirls aged 15, a Swiss woman aged 22,
OL,8,Fa Swiss and French woman aged 24, two
OL,9,FItalian girls aged 16 and 15, an
OL,10,FItalian boy aged 16, a 22-year-old
OL,11,FPortuguese woman, a 17-year-old
OL,12,FBelgian girl, two French women aged 33
OL,13,Fand 26, two French men aged 23 and 20,
OL,14,Ftwo French teenage boys aged 17 and
OL,15,F14, and a 15-year-old girl with
OL,16,FFrench, British, and Israeli
OL,17,Fnationalities, police said.
OL,19,FHundreds of people gathered in Crans-
OL,20,FMontana on Sunday to honour those
OL,21,Fkilled in the fire.
