OL,11,FThere was a chapel ceremony followed
OL,12,Fby a march, in near total silence, to
OL,13,Fthe bar where the fire took place.
OL,15,FAt one point, the crowd broke into
OL,16,Fsustained applause as flower bouquets
OL,17,Fwere laid at a makeshift memorial.
OL,19,F"We are going through a moment of
OL,20,Fcrushing darkness, but we are going
OL,21,Fthrough it together," one speaker said.
