OL,6,FSwiss authorities said they had opened
OL,7,Fa criminal investigation into the
OL,8,Fmanagers of the bar.
OL,10,FThe two managers are suspected of
OL,11,Fnegligent homicide, negligent bodily
OL,12,Fharm and causing fire by negligence,
OL,13,Fpolice said in a statement.
OL,15,FAuthorities previously stated that
OL,16,Fthey would investigate whether the
OL,17,Fmaterial on the ceiling of the venue,
OL,18,Fdesigned to muffle sound, conformed to
OL,19,Fsafety regulations.
